  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients who presented with upper gastrointestinal symptoms and endoscopically proven
             H.pylori-positive functional dyspepsia and scarred peptic ulcer

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  patients with peptic ulcer, previous H.pylori eradication therapy, previous gastric
             surgery, pregnancy, lactation, major systemic diseases, receipt of anti-secretory
             therapy, antibiotics or bismuth in the preceding 4 weeks, or allergy to any one of the
             medications
      </textblock>
